The production of this set is second to none at this juncture. Genuine 
Masters has eclipsed the other releases of this new low gen source by 
a hair. The clarity is stunning and the PCM Stereo Audio, superb. The 
concert itself is well known so there's no need to comment on that. It's 
not the best performance by the band but having this entire concert in 
this quality is such a treat. This version is absolutely complete and 
beautiful from start to finish. The Menus are gorgeous and it's simply 
a perfect transfer to DVD. Nice job. NB from Underground Uprising
